1
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:00,640
Mrs. Gu,

2
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:03,320
why did you dress Yijun as a boy?

3
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:05,560
Also,

4
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:07,260
where did Yijun come from?

5
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,280
This is the statement

6
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:19,000
from the matchmaker who introduced

7
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,440
you to Gu Dachuan.

8
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,680
She also told us

9
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,300
that you can't have children.

10
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,560
At this point,

11
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,340
there's nothing left to hide.

12
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:41,280
Yijun really was picked up.

13
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:42,520
And I...

14
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,360
I really can't have children.

15
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,280
That is why

16
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:49,000
my ex-husband's family

17
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,479
never treated me well.

18
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,080
Why did you cook so much food?

19
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,720
Money doesn't grow on trees.

20
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,960
It's the Mid-Autumn Festival today,

21
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,320
so I made an extra dish.

22
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,400
Eating so much

23
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,860
won't help me have a child.

24
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,560
I heard everything

25
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,600
that Mother said yesterday.

26
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:38,200
Mother is right.

27
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,490
Our family line cannot end.

28
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,210
Why don't you

29
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,330
find another woman to have a child?

30
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,650
As long as you don't divorce me.

31
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,040
Maybe Heaven took pity on me

32
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,920
and let me meet Yijun.

33
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:26,000
Along.

34
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,800
A baby.

35
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,280
We have a child.

36
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,840
Where did this child come from?

37
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,500
I found him.

38
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,050
At the temple entrance.

39
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,240
Didn't you and Mom

40
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,560
always want a child?

41
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,600
Are you out of your mind?

42
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:45,120
If I want a child, I want my own.

43
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,000
What good is a foundling?

44
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:50,840
I can barely feed myself,

45
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,880
let alone raise someone else's kid.

46
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:56,000
If you want to raise her, do it yourself.

47
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,170
Don't be afraid.

48
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,000
Let's sit down.

49
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:08,080
Looking at Yijun's little face,

50
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:10,040
I felt like she was my own.

51
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,840
Even if I left that home,

52
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,440
I would never abandon Yijun.

53
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,940
Later, I worked odd jobs everywhere,

54
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:21,970
carrying Yijun on my back wherever I went.

55
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,400
As long as she grows up healthy,

56
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,840
I don't mind the hardship.

57
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,200
Then why did you dress her as a boy?

58
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,000
You're a woman, too.

59
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,400
You should know

60
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,560
that for a woman to survive in this world,

61
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,690
is incredibly hard.

62
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,520
To keep her safe,

63
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,840
I dressed her as a boy

64
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,570
and named her Yijun.

65
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,120
Does Gu Dachuan know

66
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,780
that Yijun is actually a girl?

67
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,720
He knows.

68
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:56,440
I told him before we got married.

69
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,480
I also told him

70
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,920
that I couldn't have children.

71
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,780
Didn't he mind?

72
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,480
He said he already has a son,

73
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,960
and now he has a daughter, too.

74
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,440
He said that's enough.

75
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,640
We couldn't afford another one anyway.

76
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,520
Then why do you

77
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:18,160
always dress her as a boy?

78
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:24,040
Yijun was already older by then.

79
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:27,440
All the neighbors think she's a boy.

80
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,850
If she goes back to being a girl,

81
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:32,580
there will definitely be a lot of gossip.

82
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,760
So,

83
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,840
Dachuan and I decided

84
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,360
to work for a few more years,

85
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,320
then go back to his hometown to build a house.

86
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,400
By then,

87
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,280
Yijun can go back to being a girl.

88
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,440
Yijun...

89
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,360
Does she know

90
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,560
that she was adopted?

91
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,960
Of course she doesn't know.

92
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,360
There's no need for that.

93
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,320
You must not tell her.

94
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:53,320
She's still young. She's only nine.

95
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,040
Mrs. Gu.

96
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,940
Have you ever thought that

97
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,540
Yijun might be Leng Fang's daughter?

98
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,560
Impossible.

99
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,280
How is that possible?

100
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,560
But the birthmark on Yijun's back

101
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,160
and the one on Leng Fang's daughter's back

102
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,240
are exactly the same.

103
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:12,680
Impossible.

104
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,210
This must be a coincidence.

105
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:16,040
There are so many people with birthmarks in the world.

106
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,960
How can you conclude she is Leng Fang's daughter?

107
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,120
Only you know if it's a coincidence.

108
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,600
Mrs. Gu,

109
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,440
we'll give you some time to think it over.

110
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:26,440
Think it through before you tell us.

111
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:44,520
Hello.

112
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,840
Excuse me, are you

113
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:49,730
Zeng Xiaoyi's ex-husband?

114
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:50,760
What do

115
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:51,800
you want?

116
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,880
We're from the Central Police Station.

117
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,610
We have a few questions for you.

118
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,760
When did Zeng Xiaoyi leave?

119
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,760
It was

120
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:03,920
eight years ago,

121
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:06,040
on the Mid-Autumn Festival.

122
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:07,960
Why did she leave?

123
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,960
She couldn't have children.

124
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,600
She found a child somewhere.

125
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,360
I refused to raise it,

126
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,220
so she ran away.

127
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,650
What happened then?

128
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:20,210
You didn't look for her?

129
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,960
It makes me angry just talking about it.

130
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,920
Around here, men divorce women.

131
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:26,660
Women don't just run away.

132
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,290
She ran away,

133
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:30,640
and I couldn't hold my head up in public.

134
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:36,360
Thank you for your cooperation.

135
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,120
Yijun,

136
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,679
do you trust me?

137
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,520
Shengnan.

138
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:01,880
Shengnan.

139
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,320
It's

140
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:10,400
Mom.

141
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,200
Are you sure?

142
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:17,920
My own child,

143
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,880
how could I not recognize her?

144
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,920
Shengnan.

145
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,040
I am...

146
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:34,000
I'm the mother.

147
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,600
Now can you tell us

148
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,960
where Gu Yitong is?

149
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,650
Who are you looking for?

150
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,480
How are you related to this child?

151
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,640
My friend left him with me.

152
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,400
She asked me to watch him for a few days.

153
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,200
Take her away.

154
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,440
What are you doing?

155
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,080
What is your name?

156
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:18,160
My name is Gu Yitong.

157
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,200
Tongtong.

158
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:35,600
Tongtong.

159
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:36,600
Tongtong.

160
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,560
Mommy.

161
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,120
Let me see if you're hurt.

162
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:43,080
Don't worry.

163
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:45,540
Leng Fang took good care of the child.

164
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,920
Have you really thought it through?

165
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,980
Is there anything you want to tell us?

166
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,290
Yijun is Leng Fang's daughter.

167
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,080
But she's my daughter, too.

168
00:11:05,160 --> 00:11:07,220
You have no right to decide for Yijun.

169
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:10,080
You took her away from her birth mother.

170
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:12,450
What will she think when she finds out?

171
00:11:12,640 --> 00:11:14,500
I wasn't the one who took her away.

172
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:16,720
I just...

173
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,640
I just didn't want...

174
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:20,600
you to take her away from me.

175
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,760
When did you find out

176
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,890
that Gu Yijun is Leng Fang's daughter?

177
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,120
It was...

178
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:30,180
the day Leng Fang went to see Dachuan.

179
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,600
Didn't you sell her back then?

180
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,320
Go ask.

181
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,560
Let's buy her back.

182
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:34,960
There's nothing to ask.

183
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,420
Her daughter wasn't sold.

184
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,040
I abandoned her.

185
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,280
Zhongqiu.

186
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:47,680
You left her at the temple gate.

187
00:11:49,560 --> 00:11:51,240
At first, I didn't believe it,

188
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,360
so I followed Dachuan to the ruined temple.

189
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:01,060
Don't try to fool me with just anyone.

190
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,920
On my daughter's back,

191
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:06,050
there is a birthmark the size of a bowl.

192
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,400
I'll give you seven days.

193
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,040
In seven days,

194
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,000
bring my daughter to me.

195
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,890
After hearing what Leng Fang said,

196
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,690
I started to get scared.

197
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,380
Scared of what?

198
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,440
Were you afraid Gu Dachuan

199
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:22,370
would trade Gu Yijun for Gu Yitong?

200
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,480
How did Gu Dachuan know

201
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:26,610
that Gu Yijun is Leng Fang's daughter?

202
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:29,400
I thought as long as I didn't say anything, it would be fine.

203
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:32,000
I didn't expect that he had already guessed it.

204
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,970
Let's go to the police station.

205
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,720
You came just in time.

206
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,000
Tell me,

207
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,920
where did you find Yijun?

208
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:54,640
It was at the temple gate, wasn't it?

209
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:55,680
No.

210
00:12:56,920 --> 00:12:57,560
No.

211
00:12:58,680 --> 00:12:59,760
You told me

212
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:02,040
you ran away on the Mid-Autumn Festival.

213
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:02,840
On Yijun's back,

214
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,800
there's a birthmark the size of a bowl.

215
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,000
She was at the temple gate

216
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:06,840
when you found her, right?

217
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:07,400
No.

218
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:08,840
No.

219
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:11,480
I didn't find Yijun at the temple gate.

220
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,160
No.

221
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,800
I didn't find her at a temple.

222
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:14,480
No.

223
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,120
No, no.

224
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,320
It wasn't at a temple.

225
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:18,690
Where are you going?

226
00:13:20,160 --> 00:13:21,890
I'm going to get Tongtong back.

227
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,720
No, this is my daughter.

228
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:25,840
Zeng Xiaoyi.

229
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:26,800
Wake up.

230
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,600
Yijun is not your daughter.

231
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,720
She is Leng Fang's daughter.

232
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,560
I don't care.

233
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,160
For all these years,

234
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:35,360
I raised her with my own sweat and tears.

235
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:37,480
If I say she's my daughter,

236
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,840
then she is my daughter.

237
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:42,200
You can't go.

238
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:42,720
Dachuan,

239
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,160
let go.

240
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:43,680
No.

241
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:44,280
Let go.

242
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:44,760
No.

243
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,520
No.

244
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:48,080
Zeng Xiaoyi.

245
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,640
How many times have I told you?

246
00:13:49,640 --> 00:13:51,000
Yijun is not your daughter.

247
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,040
She is Leng Fang's daughter.

248
00:13:52,040 --> 00:13:52,560
Do you hear me?

249
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:53,880
No. That's not true.

250
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:55,040
Tongtong is my only son.

251
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:56,100
My biological son.

252
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,680
I must bring him back.

253
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:58,880
I must bring him back.

254
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:02,000
I was the one who brought Yijun home.

255
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,640
I raised her

256
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:04,920
all by myself.

257
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,040
When she was sick,

258
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:08,400
I was the one by her side.

259
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:10,480
Tell me,

260
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,360
is she my daughter or not?

261
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,040
What about Leng Fang?

262
00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:15,600
She could have been

263
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:17,440
like a normal mother,

264
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:18,520
with her own child.

265
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:19,840
Do you know these past eight years,

266
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,300
what she has been through?

267
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,920
Yijun.

268
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:34,760
Mom.

269
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:35,720
Yijun.

270
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,440
Shengnan.

271
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:38,360
Yijun.

272
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:39,800
Shengnan.

273
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:41,520
Mom.

274
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,400
Yijun.

275
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:43,080
Shengnan.

276
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,240
Mom.

277
00:14:44,520 --> 00:14:45,440
Shengnan.

278
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,040
Yijun.

279
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:50,280
Mom.

280
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,720
Mom.

281
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:53,880
Yijun.

282
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,880
Mom.

283
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:20,650
I never thought solving an abduction case

284
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:23,020
would feel worse than not solving it.

285
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:25,640
Zeng Xiaoyi really

286
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:28,080
gave everything for Gu Yijun.

287
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:37,800
What's on your mind, Detective Lin?

288
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:39,810
I was just thinking.

289
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:43,050
They lived together for so many years.

290
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:45,600
Gu Dachuan actually had feelings

291
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,200
for Zeng Xiaoyi and Gu Yijun.

292
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,560
He wouldn't turn murderous

293
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:50,890
over a single argument.

294
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,680
After all, Gu Yitong

295
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:55,640
is Gu Dachuan's biological son.

296
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:58,800
That's true.

297
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,800
But in that situation,

298
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:03,330
Gu Dachuan wouldn't have killed Zeng Xiaoyi.

299
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:06,120
On the other hand, for Zeng Xiaoyi,

300
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:08,280
once the truth came out,

301
00:16:08,760 --> 00:16:10,620
she'd be the one losing the child.

302
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,280
That makes sense.

303
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:18,290
Let's go back to the ruined temple.

304
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:19,960
Okay.

305
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:35,200
No.

306
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:37,300
The position is wrong.

307
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:39,040
If Gu Dachuan was killed

308
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:41,040
while strangling Zeng Xiaoyi,

309
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:44,010
the hammer shouldn't have landed so far away.

310
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:45,400
You mean

311
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:47,840
Gu Dachuan's death wasn't an accident?

312
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:48,800
Right.

313
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,850
The hammer was just a decoy.

314
00:16:50,880 --> 00:16:53,210
If Gu Dachuan's death wasn't an accident,

315
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:55,570
then Zeng Xiaoyi must have killed him.

316
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,320
The wound on Gu Dachuan's head

317
00:16:58,320 --> 00:17:00,440
indicates blunt force trauma,

318
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:03,080
but we can't confirm it was this hammer.

319
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:05,290
So we've been misled all along.

320
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:08,040
If the hammer isn't the murder weapon,

321
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:09,970
there are too many possibilities.

322
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:15,540
No matter what lies Zeng Xiaoyi told,

323
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:17,000
she must have overheard

324
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:19,319
Gu Dachuan and Leng Fang's conversation

325
00:17:19,319 --> 00:17:20,720
before deciding to kill.

326
00:17:21,040 --> 00:17:23,240
Then she couldn't have brought the weapon with her.

327
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:26,240
The weapon must be something from this ruined temple.

328
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:39,600
Come here.

329
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:40,480
Look at this.

330
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,570
It looks like blood.

331
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:50,420
That must be it.

332
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:53,280
Zeng Xiaoyi caught Gu Dachuan off guard

333
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:55,360
and smashed him to death with this rock.

334
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:56,920
Then got the hammer down

335
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,050
and staged an accident.

336
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:03,180
How many times have I told you?

337
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:04,400
Yijun isn't your daughter.

338
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:05,360
She's Leng Fang's daughter.

339
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,120
Do you hear me?

340
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:07,120
No, no.

341
00:18:07,120 --> 00:18:08,450
Tongtong is my only son.

342
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:09,560
My own son.

343
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,080
I have to bring him back.

344
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:12,140
Tongtong is my son.

345
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:12,960
My biological son.

346
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:13,800
No.

347
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:16,040
No.

348
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:19,320
No.

349
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:25,960
No.

350
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:05,720
Zeng Xiaoyi wanted to stop Gu Yijun from leaving,

351
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:07,120
so she killed Gu Dachuan.

352
00:19:08,080 --> 00:19:11,080
But Gu Yijun still recognized Leng Fang as his mother.

353
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,080
Oh no.

354
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:14,360
Leng Fang is in danger.
